Ecology.Habitats:
At depths greater than {{SI|50|ft}}, giant sea anemones were typically found solitarily. In tidal pools and secluded shorelines, smaller varieties of them could be found in groups numbering up to fifty or even two hundred. These smaller varieties would fasten themselves to rocks.

These creatures could be found in the [[Sea of Fallen Stars]].{{Cite dungeon/79/The Akriloth|82}}

Beyond [[Toril]], they could be found in the oceans of the planet [[Krynn]].
